    public class AFSwinxPanel
extends javax.swing.JPanel
    This is AFSwinx implementation of JPanel. It holds data holder, message, and another fields which are needed to construct component and maintain it during life cycle.
    Since:
    1.0.0.
    Author:
    Martin Tomasek (martin@toms-cz.com)
